quizzes.textContent:
[h1]The background-image Property[/h1]

Background-image can be set not only for the whole page, but for individual elements, as well. 
Below we set a background image for the <p> element. 

[b]The HTML:[/b] [code format="html" ]<p>This paragraph has a background image.</p>[/code]
[b]The CSS:[/b] [code format="css" codeId="547"]p {
   padding: 30px;
   background-image: url("green_photo.jpg");
   color: white;   
}[/code]
[b]Result:[/b] [img id="2627" width="100%"]
[note]To specify more than one image, just separate the URLs with [b]commas[/b].[/note]
